                 Street Figher - Round One - Fight (2009)                
 Plot

The popular Capcom video game franchise comes home in this adventure following world famous fighters Ryu and Ken on their mission to investigate the murder of their legendary martial arts master. Arriving in Japan on the trail of a killer, the two seasoned fighters realize that they're being watched not only by sadistic dictator M. Bison, but by his powerful minions as well. Now, as Cammy, Vega, and Saget shadow Ryu and Ken's every move, Hong Kong Interpol agent Chun-Li and Special Ops officer Guile watch from the sidelines, patiently awaiting the perfect moment to bring down M. Bison's malevolent Shadaloo syndicate once and for all
